article.headline: Copin St. 64, N. Carolina A&T 58
article.story: GREENSBORO, N.C. (AP) -- Tywain McKee scored 26 points and Brian Chestnut had nine rebounds Saturday to lead Coppin State to a 64-58 Mid-Eastern Athletic Conference win over N.C. A&T. The Eagles (8-17, 6-7 MEAC) also were helped by Ethan Kennedy with 11 points. Robert Pressey had seven rebounds. Steven Rush had 11 points and was the only player in double points for the Aggies (11-15, 7-7). Jason Wills had eight points and eight rebounds. Greg Roberts also had eight rebounds for the Aggies. The Eagles led 31-27 at the half.
